329
00:20:49,060 --> 00:20:50,180
You definitely did.

330
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:51,820
How else could you have a nosebleed?

331
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:56,780
Look up.

332
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:02,500
If you feel uncomfortable,

333
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:04,060
