334
00:21:06,860 --> 00:21:08,900
I want dad to come with me.

335
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:11,500
Am I not good enough for you?

336
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:12,500
All the other kids

337
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:14,580
