345
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:28,890
I… you…

346
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:32,800
Hu Ziyuan!

347
00:21:34,140 --> 00:21:34,980
Qin Can.

348
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:36,700
