371
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:44,780
Thank you, Director.

372
00:22:45,780 --> 00:22:46,620
By the way,

373
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:48,780
I heard Ning Yue's working in your company.

374
00:22:49,010 --> 00:22:50,100
How is she doing?

375
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,280
She's doing well.

376
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:54,140
Director,

377
00:22:55,140 --> 00:22:58,020
what did Ning Yue go through
