381
00:23:08,340 --> 00:23:09,900
claiming that

382
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:11,420
she had serious mental health issues.

383
00:23:11,620 --> 00:23:12,460
But Ning Yue said

384
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:14,380
she had no idea about this at all.

385
00:23:15,020 --> 00:23:16,140
If that's true,

386
00:23:16,180 --> 00:23:17,130
then her husband

387
00:23:17,130 --> 00:23:19,300
