with his own hands.

388
00:23:25,340 --> 00:23:26,540
What a bad teacher you are!

389
00:23:26,550 --> 00:23:27,740
Call the parents over here.

390
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:28,740
Sir, calm down.

391
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:29,770
Control your kid!

392
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:31,820
Sir.

393
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:32,920
Ziyuan.

394
00:23:33,330 --> 00:23:34,550
- What do you want to do?
- What's going on?

395
00:23:34,550 --> 00:23:35,710
- Is everything okay?
- What happened?

396
00:23:36,140 --> 00:23:39,260
Mom, Xiao Hu bullied Qin Jiaojiao first.

397
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:40,980
You're the kid's parent, right?

398
00:23:40,980 --> 00:23:42,820
Why is your kid bullying mine?

399
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:44,380
Nonsense.

400
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:45,980
- Make it clear.
- Educate your child

401
00:23:46,220 --> 00:23:47,100
or I…

402
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:49,340
- Stop!
- Don't start a fight!

403
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,740
- Calm down!
- Back off!

404
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:53,060
- Just stop!
- Mom, are you okay?

405
00:23:53,060 --> 00:23:54,340
I'm fine.

406
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:56,060
Let's call the police.

407
00:23:56,420 --> 00:23:57,260
Sure.

408
00:23:57,900 --> 00:24:03,700
(Bindao City Police Station)

409
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:04,620
Director Qin,

410
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:05,900
thanks a lot today.

411
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:07,580
- Never mind.
- Sorry for the trouble.

412
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:11,300
Hu Ziyuan,

413
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:16,180
on behalf of Qin Jiaojiao's parents, thank you.

414
00:24:16,930 --> 00:24:18,700
You're righteous and brave.

415
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:20,260
You're a good boy.

416
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:21,980
Jiaojiao is lucky

417
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,100
to have a friend like you.

418
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,260
Thank you, Little Uncle Qin.

419
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:27,460
We'll always be good friends.

420
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,470
We'll always be good friends.

421
00:24:31,260 --> 00:24:32,100
Well,

422
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,220
let's go.

423
00:24:33,450 --> 00:24:34,290
Let's go.

424
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:46,820
Dad!

425
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:50,140
Ziyuan.

426
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:54,620
Why are you guys so late getting back?

427
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:57,140
Honey.

428
00:24:57,940 --> 00:24:58,780
Honey!

429
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:00,260
Why are you ignoring me?

430
00:25:00,620 --> 00:25:01,940
I tried calling, but you didn't pick up.

431
00:25:02,180 --> 00:25:03,540
Do you know how worried I was?

432
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,420
I almost called the police earlier.

433
00:25:07,430 --> 00:25:09,020
We just came back
from the police station.

434
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:12,820
What happened?

435
00:25:13,290 --> 00:25:14,130
What's going on?

436
00:25:14,300 --> 00:25:15,590
Dad,

437
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:17,940
I fought with Li Xiaohu.

438
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:20,460
That's the reason?

439
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:26,300
Ziyuan,

440
00:25:26,540 --> 00:25:27,380
tell me,

441
00:25:27,700 --> 00:25:28,540
did you start the fight,

442
00:25:28,540 --> 00:25:29,780
or the other way around?

443
00:25:29,980 --> 00:25:31,820
He bullied me first.

444
00:25:46,850 --> 00:25:48,140
Zi Yuan has nosebleed again.

445
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:49,540
Again?

446
00:25:50,130 --> 00:25:51,580
It's fine, already stopped.

447
00:25:56,020 --> 00:25:56,860
Honey,

448
00:26:00,100 --> 00:26:00,940
what happened?

449
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:02,980
What happened to your foot?

450
00:26:05,940 --> 00:26:07,060
Why have you had the bruise?

451
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:11,020
I'm good.

452
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,780
- Bye.
- Bye.

453
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:17,680
Bye.

454
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:21,380
The police's taken Li Xiaohu's father
in for questioning.

455
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:22,220
What?

456
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:23,500
- For real?
- Ms. Li.

457
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:24,420
Ziyuan's here.

458
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,820
- Go inside.
- Goodbye, Mom.

459
00:26:25,940 --> 00:26:26,780
See you.

460
00:26:31,020 --> 00:26:32,030
Ms. Li.

461
00:26:32,270 --> 00:26:33,540
What are they saying?

462
00:26:33,540 --> 00:26:34,700
What happened?

463
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:37,090
Something happened to Li Xiaohu's family.

464
00:26:37,790 --> 00:26:40,160
His dad was taken in by the police last night.

465
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:41,880
They don't know why yet.

466
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:44,280
So his grandma sent him to school today.

467
00:26:44,660 --> 00:26:46,140
I heard from other parents that

468
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:49,020
his dad was reported for an economic crime.

469
00:26:50,380 --> 00:26:51,740
I see. Thank you, Ms. Li.

470
00:27:03,690 --> 00:27:04,660
Honey,

471
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:06,700
you left something behind?

472
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:08,540
The kindergarten teacher said

473
00:27:08,540 --> 00:27:09,380
Li Xiaohu's dad

474
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:10,780
was taken away by the police.

475
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:12,980
Isn't that a good thing?

476
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:14,940
It's karma.

477
00:27:16,020 --> 00:27:17,100
He's such a thug,

478
00:27:17,540 --> 00:27:18,940
doing so many bad things,

479
00:27:19,380 --> 00:27:20,550
and now, any small thing

480
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,660
could get him arrested.

481
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:25,500
Honey,

482
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,780
I'll never let anyone

483
00:27:29,260 --> 00:27:31,140
hurt you and Ziyuan.

484
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:35,940
You don't let anyone

485
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:37,460
bully your wife and son,

486
00:27:38,900 --> 00:27:40,180
but you're fine with doing it yourself?

487
00:27:43,620 --> 00:27:44,460
Mr. Hu,

488
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,620
Mr. Zhou and the others have arrived,

489
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:49,100
they're waiting for us.

490
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:53,820
Let's talk later.

491
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:11,660
He's just planning to deny everything,

492
00:28:12,490 --> 00:28:14,530
pretending like nothing happened,

493
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,220
and trying to get away with it.

494
00:28:17,850 --> 00:28:18,940
But it's okay,

495
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:19,780
it doesn't matter

496
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,660
whether he admits it or not.

497
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:22,900
Tonight,

498
00:28:23,690 --> 00:28:25,180
I'm definitely going to get a divorce.

499
00:28:27,970 --> 00:28:29,060
What are you worried about?

500
00:28:30,730 --> 00:28:31,820
I'm worried about

501
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:33,780
that Ziyuan...

502
00:28:35,660 --> 00:28:37,100
He's not willing to leave his dad.

503
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:44,980
Ning Yue,

504
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:48,140
do you want your child

505
00:28:48,420 --> 00:28:49,780
to grow up to be like him?

506
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:56,580
This restaurant is so good,

507
00:28:56,580 --> 00:28:57,940
I usually don't treat myself to it.

508
00:28:58,580 --> 00:29:00,220
I came here just for this.

509
00:29:01,380 --> 00:29:02,300
It's pretty fresh.

510
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:11,580
Yue, is there something to celebrate today?

511
00:29:11,580 --> 00:29:12,540
You're already drinking.

512
00:29:12,540 --> 00:29:14,260
Come on, let's drink together.

513
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:25,300
I'll be free.

514
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:27,180
You'll be free?

515
00:29:27,980 --> 00:29:30,100
Are you gonna send Ziyuan to your parents?

516
00:29:31,780 --> 00:29:33,060
Come on, cheers.

517
00:29:33,780 --> 00:29:34,700
To freedom.

518
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:35,740
To freedom.

519
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:43,060
They're always

520
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:44,700
playing like crazy together.

521
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:46,900
Look at Ziyuan,

522
00:29:47,300 --> 00:29:48,340
he's growing so fast.

523
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:50,820
He's shorter than Tongtong before.

524
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:55,820
When it comes to staying at your home,

525
00:29:55,820 --> 00:29:57,180
he gets so excited.

526
00:29:57,460 --> 00:29:59,060
You should come over more often.

527
00:29:59,260 --> 00:30:01,100
My wife loves playing with kids.

528
00:30:07,540 --> 00:30:08,380
Wei,

529
00:30:10,340 --> 00:30:11,700
