530
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:14,060
You really haven't realized that.

531
00:30:16,460 --> 00:30:17,780
I misjudged before.

532
00:30:18,620 --> 00:30:20,140
Yue is really generous.

533
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:21,380
She doesn't hold grudges,

534
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:22,580
and didn't make a big fuss.

535
00:30:23,980 --> 00:30:24,900
Tonight,

536
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:27,540
you should apologize to her.

537
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:29,540
She really treats you well.

538
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:32,340
Don't take her for granted.

539
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:34,100
Don't blame me for saying too much.

540
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:36,140
You've already failed in marriage once.

541
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:37,700
You can't go through that again.

542
00:30:39,940 --> 00:30:42,020
Even if you glare at me, I'll still speak out.

543
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:47,580
Yue is different from your ex-wife.

544
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:55,220
Wei,

545
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:58,220
I have always had

546
00:30:59,380 --> 00:31:00,660
only one wife,

547
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:03,140
Ning Yue.

548
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:05,460
Alright.

549
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:08,620
As long as you keep it to yourself.

550
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:20,020
Drink up.

551
00:31:20,210 --> 00:31:21,060
We'll drink more later.

552
00:31:21,060 --> 00:31:22,260
Later.

553
00:31:24,900 --> 00:31:26,460
Manager Tian got promoted

554
00:31:27,300 --> 00:31:28,140
