556
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,340
Forget it.

557
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:36,900
Just live your life well.

558
00:31:40,780 --> 00:31:42,260
I remember now.

559
00:31:42,580 --> 00:31:44,580
I saw you in an industry magazine.

560
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:47,060
When I was a freshman,

561
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,380
